{
  "text": "In the following we assume that we have constructed a mapping U(k) from N Bloch states computed by Wien2k [CITATION_1] to N maximally localized Wannier functions (WFs) with Wannier90 [CITATION_2] ; thus we have the Hamiltonian in Wannier space",
